Interface TTConfig

All Superinterfaces:
MRConfig
@InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface TTConfig
extends MRConfig

Place holder for TaskTracker server-level configuration. The keys should have "mapreduce.tasktracker." as the prefix
